class DeferredRun {
public:
        DeferredRun(const std::function<void()>& run) : _run(run) { }
        ~DeferredRun() {
                _run();
        }
private:
        const std::function<void()> _run;
};

int main(int argc, char* argv[])
{
        auto hFile = OpenHandle(argv[1]);

        DeferredRun deferredRun([&]() {
                CloseHandle(hFile);
        });
